title: Chapter V - State University of New York
content:
Chapter V - State University of New York

State Regulations

Subchapter A - Regulations of the Board of Trustees (Part 300 to 316)

Subchapter B - Policies of the Board of Trustees (Part 325 to 400)

Subchapter C - Administration and Operation of State-operated Institutions of State University of New York (Article 1 to 4)

Subchapter D - Code of Standards and Procedures for the Administration and Operation of Community Colleges under the Program of State University of New York (Part 600 to 850)

Subchapter E - Regulations of the Board of Trustees' Charter Schools Committee (Part 700)

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
